139
00:17:01,854 --> 00:17:04,438
Natasha Romanoff.

140
00:17:06,518 --> 00:17:08,190
Are you here to kill me, Miss Romanoff?

141
00:17:08,035 --> 00:17:11,035
Because that's not gonna
work out for everyone.

142
00:17:11,071 --> 00:17:14,103
No. No. Of course not.
I'm here on behalf of SHIELD.

143
00:17:15,411 --> 00:17:19,573
SHIELD. How did they find me?

144
00:17:19,706 --> 00:17:22,592
We never lost you, doctor.
We've kept our distance,

145
00:17:22,726 --> 00:17:26,385
even helped keep some
other interested parties off your scent.

146
00:17:26,519 --> 00:17:30,009
- Why?
- Nick Fury seems to trust you.

147
00:17:30,142 --> 00:17:32,492
But now I need you to come in.

148
00:17:32,827 --> 00:17:37,157
- What if I say no?
- I'll persuade you.

149
00:17:39,137 --> 00:17:43,129
And what if the...other guy says no?

150
00:17:44,135 --> 00:17:45,759
You've been more than a
year without an incident.

151
00:17:45,759 --> 00:17:47,863
