152
00:17:50,880 --> 00:17:53,869
I don't get every time what I want.

153
00:17:54,504 --> 00:17:58,297
Doctor, we're facing a
potential global catastrophe.

154
00:17:58,430 --> 00:18:02,759
- Well, those I actively try to avoid.
- This is the

155
00:18:03,363 --> 00:18:05,646
Tesseract.

156
00:18:05,780 --> 00:18:09,639
It has the potential energy
to wipe out the planet.

157
00:18:11,652 --> 00:18:13,049
