158
00:18:13,049 --> 00:18:16,250
Well, he wants you to find it. It's been taken.

159
00:18:17,425 --> 00:18:21,653
It omits a gamma signature
that's too weak for us to trace.

160
00:18:21,788 --> 00:18:24,706
There's no one that knows
gamma radiation like you do.

161
00:18:24,840 --> 00:18:28,261
If there was, that's where I'd be.

162
00:18:28,399 --> 00:18:32,122
- So Fury isn't after the monster?
- Not that he's told me.

163
00:18:32,257 --> 00:18:34,707
And he tells you everything?

164
00:18:35,075 --> 00:18:37,726
- Talk to Fury, he needs you on this.
- He needs me in a cage?

165
00:18:37,860 --> 00:18:41,150
- No one's gonna put you in a...
- Stop lying to me!

166
