174
00:19:21,721 --> 00:19:24,372
You're dealing with
forces you can't control.

175
00:19:24,504 --> 00:19:28,030
You ever been in a war,
Councilman? In a firefight?

176
00:19:28,163 --> 00:19:30,914
Did you feel an over abundance of control?

177
00:19:31,049 --> 00:19:34,471
You saying that this Asgard has
declared war on our planet?

178
00:19:34,605 --> 00:19:37,290
Not Asgard. Loki.

179
00:19:37,425 --> 00:19:41,282
He can't be working alone.
What about the other one? His brother.

180
00:19:41,418 --> 00:19:43,599
Our intelligence says, Thor is not a hostile.

181
00:19:43,233 --> 00:19:46,233
