they can be exactly what we need.

192
00:20:19,392 --> 00:20:24,678
- You believe?
- War isn't won by sentiment, Director.

193
00:20:25,250 --> 00:20:28,928
No, it's won by soldiers.

194
00:20:48,069 --> 00:20:52,352
