I think I've had my fill.

199
00:21:34,382 --> 00:21:39,133
Then you should be out,
celebrating, seeing the world.

200
00:21:44,186 --> 00:21:47,030
I went under, the world was at war,

201
00:21:47,231 --> 00:21:51,815
